Package dk.via.sep.client.core

Class ViewHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • dk.via.sep.client.core.ViewHandler
  • public class ViewHandler
extends java.lang.Object
    The class responsible for managing the views of the program, and switching between them. It contains methods for each view, as well as implementing the singleton design pattern so it can be used throughout the program.
